ATTRIBUTION REQUIREMENT (MANDATORY)
=============================================================================

In addition to the above MIT License terms, any use, modification, or
distribution of this software or derivative works thereof MUST include
visible and prominent attribution to:

    - Author: sunba91
    - Project: OID (OpenVPN Isolated Docker)
    - Source: https://github.com/sunba91-su/oid

This attribution must be:

1. VISIBLE: Displayed in a manner that is easily noticed by end users
   (e.g., in documentation, About pages, UI credits, or README files)

2. PROMINENT: Not hidden in fine print, footnotes, or non-obvious locations

3. ACCURATE: Correctly identify the original author and project name

4. COMPLETE: Include all three elements (author, project name, source URL)

Acceptable forms of attribution include, but are not limited to:

- "Powered by OID (OpenVPN Isolated Docker) by sunba91"
- "Based on OID by sunba91 (https://github.com/sunba91-su/oid)"
- "This software uses OID, created by sunba91"
- A credits section listing the above information

EXAMPLE ATTRIBUTMENT NOTATION:

    This product includes OID (OpenVPN Isolated Docker), an open-source
    project by sunba91. Source: https://github.com/sunba91-su/oid

